<p>我们在xaml创建一个Pivot</p>

<div class="language-xml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>        <span class="nt">&lt;Pivot</span> <span class="na">Grid.Row=</span><span class="s">"1"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
            <span class="nt">&lt;PivotItem</span> <span class="na">Header=</span><span class="s">"lindexi"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/PivotItem&gt;</span>
            <span class="nt">&lt;PivotItem</span> <span class="na">Header=</span><span class="s">"CSDN"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/PivotItem&gt;</span>

        <span class="nt">&lt;/Pivot&gt;</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<p>这样的Header是默认颜色</p>

<p><img src="http://image.acmx.xyz/be842536-5c96-47f4-a49d-354e749a826a20161229152841.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>我们想修改颜色，可以使用</p>

<div class="language-xml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    <span class="nt">&lt;Pivot.HeaderTemplate&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;DataTemplate&gt;</span>
            <span class="nt">&lt;TextBlock</span> <span class="na">Text=</span><span class="s">"{Binding}"</span> <span class="na">Foreground=</span><span class="s">"Cyan"</span> <span class="na">FontSize=</span><span class="s">"40"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;/DataTemplate&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;/Pivot.HeaderTemplate&gt;</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="http://image.acmx.xyz/f3c2f4a3-94ae-40b4-b3c3-da73116eb75d2016121716265.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>参见：
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/31797875/overriding-pivot-header-foreground-brushes-in-uwp-app-win-10-rtm-sdk</p>

<p>但是如果我们要修改多的Pivot，使用模板其实还不能修改不选中的Pivot Header的颜色</p>

<p>我写了一个Style，可以直接复制到需要使用Pivot的Grid资源</p>

<div class="language-xml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>        <span class="nt">&lt;Style</span> <span class="na">TargetType=</span><span class="s">"PivotHeaderItem"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
